name: Experiment Or Die #86
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Yesterdays layout was about the idea of the unknown and the search for what could be out in the Universe. Todays layout is about what happens when we are discovered by a much more advanced robotic species and they enslave humanity. Why can't the humans and the robots live in peace? Not sure humanity is meant for co-habitation with any other life on the same planet. Maybe cats and that's it. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
